overview: See what happens when three guys from the dorm get into a scuffle with three frat guys on the college wrestling team. Rather than get into a fist fight, they decide to settle their differences wrestling in the frat house basement. But when Troy's underwear gets ripped during the first match, they challenge each other to wrestling like the ancient Greeks -- in the nude.  College Wrestlers features six athletically sculpted young men in three down-for-the-count regulation matches. You'll be able to feel the heat coming off the mat as they grapple for the pin.
title: COLLEGE WRESTLERS: Manifest Fantasies Volume 1
